tilities, up to your vacate date. </p> <h6 style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Deposit Refund: </h6> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 20px;\"> Your security deposit will be assessed and refunded in accordance with the terms of your lease agreement. </p> </div> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"> If you have any questions or need further assistance, please do not hesitate to contact at our office. We appreciate your cooperation throughout your tenancy and wish you the best in your future endeavors. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 8px;\"> Greetings, </span> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 4px;\"> ${Admin_User} </span> </div> </div> </div> </div>"},{"SendTo":"Owner","TemplateName":"Vacate Inspection Report to Owner With Complaints","Subject":"Vacate Inspection Report","Message":"<div style=\"width: 750px; font-family: 'Lato', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 0px; border-style: dashed; border-color: #DDE1E5;\"> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Inspection Report </h6> <div> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Hi ${Owner_Name}, </h6> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px;\"> I am writing to inform you about the recent inspection of the ${Unit_Name}. Following the vacating tenant's departure. Below are the issues identified during the inspection. </p> </div> <div style=\"border-radius: 4px 4px 4px 4px;\"> <table style=\"width: 100%; line-height: normal; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 24px;\"> <thead> <tr> <th style=\"width: calc(100% / 3); background-color: #F9FAFE; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: #DDE1E5; border-radius: 4px 0px 0px 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: left;\"> Complaints </th> <th style=\"width:  calc(100% / 3); background-color: #F9FAFE; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: #DDE1E5; border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: left;\"> Description </th> <th style=\"width:  calc(100% / 3); background-color: #F9FAFE; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 1px; border-