aintenance cost should be covered by the owner or the tenant, as per the lease agreement and the nature of the maintenance work performed. <br><br> Please review the details and let us know your decision at your earliest convenience. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 8px;\"> Greetings, </span> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 4px;\"> ${Admin_User} </span> </div> </div> </div> </div>"},{"SendTo":"Property Management","TemplateName":"New User Added","Subject":"Welcome ${Name} to Property Management App","Message":"<div style=\"width: 750px; font-family: 'Lato', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 1px 0px 1px 0px; border-style: dashed; border-color: #DDE1E5;\"> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px;\"> New User Added as ${Role} to the Property Management </h6> <div> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Hi ${User_Name}, </h6> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; m