: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"> ${User_Name} now has access to the necessary resources and tools to perform their ${Role}  effectively. <br> <br> If you have any questions or require further information, please do not hesitate to contact us <br> <br> We are confident that ${User_Name} will be a valuable addition to our team and look forward to the contributions they will make. </p> </div> <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"> <a href=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #FFF; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 1px 1px 1px 1px; text-decoration: none; background-color: #38BB78;\">Access the Property Management</a> </div> </div> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 8px;\"> Greetings, </span> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 4px;\"> ${Admin_User} </span> </div> </div> </div> </div>"},{"SendTo":"Property Management","TemplateName":"User Removed to Property Management To User","Subject":"User Removed to Property Management","Message":"<div style=\"width: 750px; font-family: 'Lato', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px;