/tr> <tr> <td style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: left;\"> Role: </td> <td style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: left;\"> ${Role} </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <div> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"> <b>Access Revoked: The user no longer has access to the application and associated resources</b> <br> <br> If you have any questions or require further information, please do not hesitate to contact us. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 8px;\"> Greetings, </span> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 4px;\"> ${Admin_User} </span> </div> </div> </div> </div>"},{"SendTo":"Owner","TemplateName":"Agreement Activated To Owner","Subject":"Agreement Activated","Message":"<div style=\"width: 750px; font-family: 'Lato', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-b