gin-left: 0px;\"> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Current Status:</h6> <h6 style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px;\"> <span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px;\">1. </span>Owner Approval: </h6> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 50px;\"> We are pleased to inform you that the agreement has been approved by the owner. </p> <h6 style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px;\"> <span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px;\">2. </span>Tenant Rejection: </h6> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 50px;\"> Unfortunately, the agreement has been rejected by the tenant. </p> </div> <div style=\"border: 1px solid #EBECF0;border-radius: 8px;margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"> <table style=\"width: 100%; line-height: normal; border-collapse: collapse;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 10px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 20px;border-bottom: 1px solid #EBECF0;\" colspan=\"4\"> <span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.3;color: #131635;float: left;\">Agreement Details </span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;\">Agreement No </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${Agreement_No} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">Agreement Type </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${Agreement_Type} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">Property </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${Property_Name} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">Unit </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"> ${Unit_Name} </span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;\">Security Deposit </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"> ${Security_Deposit} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">Start Date </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${Start_Date} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">End Date </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${End_Date} </span> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"> <a href=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #FFF; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 1px 1px 1px 1px; text-decoration: none; background-color: #38BB78;\"> View Details </a> </div> </div> </div> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 8px;\"> Greetings, </span> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 4px;\"> ${Admin_User} </span> </div> </div> </div> </div>"},{"SendTo":"Tenant","TemplateName":"Owner Approved Vacate Request To Tenant","Subject":"Vacate Request Approved for ${Unit_Name}.","Message":"<div style=\"width: 750px; font-family: 'Lato', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 0px; border-style: dashed; border-color: #DDE1E5;\"> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Vacate Request Approved</h6> <div> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Hi ${Tenant_Name}, </h6> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"> I am pleased to inform you that your request to vacate the ${Unit_Name} has been approved. Your agreed move-out date of ${Vacate_Date} has been confirmed. <br><br> We have also coordinated with the property owner, and both parties have agreed to the terms of your vacate request. As per our agreement, the property status has been updated to reflect that it is now officially vacated. </p> </div> <div style=\"border: 1px solid #EBECF0;border-radius: 8px;margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 0px;\"> <table style=\"width: 100%; line-height: normal; border-collapse: collapse;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 10px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 20px;border-bottom: 1px solid #EBECF0;\" colspan=\"4\"> <span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.3;color: #131635;float: left;\">Agreement Details </span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;\">Agreement No </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${Agreement_No} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">Agreement Type </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${Agreement_Type} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">Property </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${Property_Name} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">Unit </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"> ${Unit_Name} </span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;\">Security Deposit </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"> ${Security_Deposit} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">Start Date </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${Start_Date} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">End Date </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${End_Date} </span> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <div> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"> If you have any questions or require assistance during your move-out process, do not hesitate to reach out to me directly. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 8px;\"> Greetings, </span> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 4px;\"> ${Admin_User} </span> </div> </div> </div> </div>"},{"SendTo":"Tenant","TemplateName":"Owner Approved Renewal Request To Tenant","Subject":"Renewal Request Approved for ${Unit_Name}.","Message":"<div style=\"width: 750px; font-family: 'Lato', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 0px; border-style: dashed; border-color: #DDE1E5;\"> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Renewal Request Approved</h6> <div> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Hi ${Tenant_Name}, </h6> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"> I am pleased to inform you that your request to renew  for the <unit> has been approved. Your Old agreement has been deactivated and new agreement will update soon. </p> </div> <div style=\"border: 1px solid #EBECF0;border-radius: 8px;margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 0px;\"> <table style=\"width: 100%; line-height: normal; border-collapse: collapse;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 10px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 20px;border-bottom: 1px solid #EBECF0;\" colspan=\"4\"> <span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.3;color: #131635;float: left;\">Agreement Details </span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;\">Agreement No </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${Agreement_No} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">Agreement Type </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${Agreement_Type} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">Property </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${Property_Name} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">Unit </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"> ${Unit_Name} </span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;\">Security Deposit </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"> ${Security_Deposit} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">Start Date </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${Start_Date} </span> </td> <td style=\"vertical-align: top;padding-top: 12px;padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;padding-left: 20px;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #3C3E44;display: block;\">End Date </span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 1.5;color: #131635;display: block;margin-top: 8px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">${End_Date} </span> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <div> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"> We appreciate you continuing as a tenant and look forward to another term. If you have any specific requests or concerns regarding the renewal, please let us know. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 8px;\"> Greetings, </span> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 4px;\"> ${Admin_User} </span> </div> </div> </div> </div>"},{"SendTo":"Property Management","TemplateName":"Payments Due Date Reminder to all","Subject":"Payments Due Date Reminder","Message":"<div style=\"width: 750px; font-family: 'Lato', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 1px 0px 1px 0px; border-style: dashed; border-color: #DDE1E5;\"> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Payments Due Date Reminder </h6> <div> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Hi ${Tenant_Name}, </h6> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px;\"> This is a reminder that the payment due date for your account has passed. As of ${Due_Date}, we have not yet received your payment. Kindly note that if the payment is not made within the current grace period of ${Penalty_Date}, a penalty will be applied to your account as per the agreed terms. Please arrange the payment at your earliest convenience to avoid any additional charges. For any questions or assistance, feel free to contact our team. <br> <br> Your payment details are below: </p> </div> <div> <table style=\"width: 100%; line-height: normal; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 20px;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: left;\"> Description: </td> <td style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: left;\"> ${Description} </td> </tr> <tr> <td style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: left;\"> Amount: </td> <td style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: left;\"> ${Amount} </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <div> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"> If you have already made the payment, please disregard this reminder. Should you have any questions or require further assistance. <br> <br> Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 8px;\"> Greetings, </span> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 4px;\"> ${Admin_User} </span> </div> </div> </div> </div>"},{"SendTo":"Property Management","TemplateName":"Penalty Amount Added To all","Subject":"Penalty Amount Added","Message":"<div style=\"width: 750px; font-family: 'Lato', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 1px 0px 1px 0px; border-style: dashed; border-color: #DDE1E5;\"> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Penalty Amount Added </h6> <div> <h6 style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px;\"> Hi ${Tenant_Name}, </h6> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px;\"> We inform you that your payment, which was due on ${Due_Date}, has not been received. As a result, a penalty has been added to your outstanding balance in accordance with our agreement. Please arrange for the full payment, including the penalty, as soon as possible to avoid further complications. If you need any assistance or clarification, feel free to contact our team. <br> <br> Your payment details are below: </p> </div> <div> <table style=\"width: 100%; line-height: normal; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 20px;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: left;\"> Description: </td> <td style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: left;\"> ${Description} </td> </tr> <tr> <td style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: left;\"> Amount: </td> <td style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #131635; text-align: left;\"> ${Amount} </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <div> <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"> If you have already made the payment, please disregard this reminder. Should you have any questions or require further assistance. <br> <br> Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter. </p> </div> </div> <div style=\"padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; padding-left: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 8px;\"> Greetings, </span> <span style=\"display: block; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1px; color: #3C3E44; margin-bottom: 4px;\"> ${Admin_User} </span> </div> </div> </div> </div>"}};
                 	return email_template_Contents;
                 }
				 map Data_Map.Image_Sources()
                 {
                 	img_src = Map();
                 	img_src.put("no_data","data:image/svg+xml;base64,");
                 	return img_src;
